snippet.textDisplay: objectively i think that this might be one of the best videos Jenna has ever done. Not only is it overflowing with love and care for all the dogs and each other, the comedic timing of all of the funny moments is the most solid it's ever been. The crocs first of all were extremely cool but then to reveal the AWFUL socks underneath just makes the moment. then, the socks appearing with no comment later in the video was a great callback that gave the video a really well-put together feeling. Finally, nothing could have ever prepared me for the end of the video, which was not only absolutely hilarious but also again full of love and care for bunny who deserves nothing less. to sum it up this video is definitely in my personal top ten videos on this channel if not on all of youtube. absolutely fantastic.
